{
  "verses": [
    {
      "verse_num": "1",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Lord, my enemies have become so many; so many are rebelling against me.\n"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "2",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "So many are telling me,"
        },
        {
          "type": "speech",
          "text": "God can't save you!",
          "speaker": "Unknown"
        },
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Selah."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "3",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "But you, Lord, are a shield protecting me. You give me victory;  you hold my head high."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "4",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I cry out to the Lord for help, and he answers me from his holy mountain. Selah."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "5",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I lie down to sleep, and in the morning I wake up because the Lord takes care of me."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "6",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "I'm not afraid of tens of thousands who surround me, people who are against me."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "7",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "St and up for me, Lord! Save me, my God! Hit all my enemies on the cheek; break the teeth of the wicked!"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "8",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Salvation belongs to you, Lord; may you be a blessing to your people. Selah."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    }
  ]
}